# Cursor Rules for Mutual Aid List

## Permissions
Full read, write, edit, delete, and execute permissions for all operations in this repository.

## Project Context
- Hugo-based static site for mutual aid requests
- Data stored as JSON files in `data/` directory
- Each entry follows schema: name, description, link, location, tags, created_at, updated_at
- Deploy to GitHub Pages via `gh-pages` branch

## Development
- Use `hugo server` for local development
- Use `hugo` to build production site
- Validate JSON files before committing
- Follow data schema requirements from CLAUDE.md

## Code Style
- Clean, minimal design
- Ensure all JSON is properly formatted
- Location format: "[City], [State Code]"
